ZYTE BACKEND

PREREQUISITES
1- Clone the following project https://github.com/typicode/json-server.git
2- Create db.jason file in the project root of the previous step, inserting the following body into it:
{
    "posts": [
        { "id": 1, "title": "json-server", "author": "typicode" }
    ],
    "comments": [
        { "id": 1, "body": "some comment", "postId": 1 }
    ],
    "profiles": [{"id": 1, "name": "typicode" }]
}
3- At the command prompt, start the database through the command json-server --watch db.json

EXECUTION MODE
1- Run  by command line using the mvn test command on the path of the project
2- Run by junit clicking on ZyteTest.Java and execute by junit
